The Haiku Requirements:
- First sentence needs to be on 5 syllabes
- Second sentence needs to be on 7 syllabes
- Third sentence needs to be on 5 syllabes
- A haiku made needs to be saved in another folder

Suggestions:
-/1 Make a counter that will go up if a vowel have been checked in a word that doesnt occure 2 times
in a row.
-/2 Make it so if it checks a consonant after a vowel to add 1 to a counter
-/1 Make it that it need to be followed up by a consonant after a vowel before it counts it as a syllabel
-/2 Make it override the current Haiku in the folder if got any time